title: Battle of Gallipoli: Layered Ottoman Defense - The Great War Mod Gameplay
description:
This is another online battle in the Great War mod for Napoleon Total War.  This is a recreation of the battle of Gallipoli not 100% historically correct.  The Ottomans prepare their defense against invading British and common wealth! Enjoy the battle :D  

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
